317"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t答：不太熟悉（刚才的时平行光的）"}]},{"ID":"20240304163318-q0rdd6y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163318-q0rdd6y","updated":"20240304163327"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.骨骼动画的原理"}]},{"ID":"20240304163327-o7om3is","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163327-o7om3is","updated":"20240304163349"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t答：骨骼运动时，具有相应权重的顶点会跟着运动"}]},{"ID":"20240304163350-6qdjowi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163350-6qdjowi","updated":"20240304163414"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.一个顶点最多被几根骨骼控制？"}]},{"ID":"20240304163416-7l1jhlw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163416-7l1jhlw","updated":"20240304163422"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t答：（一个）不会"}]},{"ID":"20240304184831-yyhpnph","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304184831-yyhpnph","updated":"20240304184832"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t解答："}]},{"ID":"20240304184842-wb0c8ky","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304184842-wb0c8ky","updated":"20240304184842"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t在3D建模和动画中，一个顶点可以被多个骨骼或骨头控制，但具体数量取决于软件或项目的具体要求。通常情况下，对于实时应用程序，如视频游戏，一个顶点通常限制受到4个骨骼的影响，这是由于硬件和性能的限制。这种限制有助于确保动画可以由图形硬件高效处理。"}]},{"ID":"20240304184842-db1r7ij","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304184842-db1r7ij","updated":"20240304184842"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"然而，在非实时应用中，如电影中的高端3D动画，一个顶点可以被超过4个骨骼影响。在这些情况下使用的软件可能允许更高的限制，但是需要平衡详细变形的需求与计算成本。"}]},{"ID":"20240304184842-3shuk5s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304184842-3shuk5s","updated":"20240304184842"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总之，虽然对于实时应用来说，每个顶点被4个骨骼控制是一个常见标准，但在其他情况下，根据软件和项目要求，限制可以更高。"}]},{"ID":"20240304163422-hh9xmyd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163422-hh9xmyd","updated":"20240304163440"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"7.当有大量顶点时如何优化骨骼动画？"}]},{"ID":"20240304163441-7tk1n2m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163441-7tk1n2m","updated":"20240304163453"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t答：烘培到GPU贴图上让GPU算。"}]},{"ID":"20240304163454-rihdpfg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163454-rihdpfg","updated":"20240304163505"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"8.为什么这么做会让动画变快？"}]},{"ID":"20240304163506-miryjvz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163506-miryjvz","updated":"20240304163536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t答：我答因为GPU与CPU架构不同，适合做并行动画。"}]},{"ID":"20240304163538-1rymd9r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163538-1rymd9r","updated":"20240304163636"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t面试官说不对，主要是因为CPU向GPU传递数据时会有耗时，烘培到贴图上可以减少这个过程"}]},{"ID":"20240304163636-6bfgbch","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163636-6bfgbch","updated":"20240304163645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"9.这么做有什么缺点？"}]},{"ID":"20240304163645-rqd5qci","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163645-rqd5qci","updated":"20240304163704"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t答：需要空间更多，需要烘培耗时"}]},{"ID":"20240304163704-iwumsod","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163704-iwumsod","updated":"20240304163742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t面试官说主要是这种无法打断，无法有事件相关的操作，无法接收事件等，局限性较大。"}]},{"ID":"20240304163742-mniep8u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163742-mniep8u","updated":"20240304163803"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"10.给两个百万级别的字符串进行比较如何优化？"}]},{"ID":"20240304163803-056b1ky","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163803-056b1ky","updated":"20240304163928"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t答：不会，面试官引导后我说将一个一个char解释成一个一个long，这样速度会翻八倍。"}]},{"ID":"20240304163929-5wrpcxj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163929-5wrpcxj","updated":"20240304163939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"11.map的key有什么要求？"}]},{"ID":"20240304163939-ht4wk9j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240304163939-ht4wk9j","u